Sec=<b>{Confidential_Information}.</b><br>{Engage.Base.Sen} {Engage.Agents.Sen} {Except.Compelled.Sen}  {3PartyQueries.Sen} 

Model.Root={Sec}

Engage.Base.Sen={1.Sen}
Engage.Agents.Sen={2.Sen}
Except.Compelled.Sen={3.Sen}
3PartyQueries.Sen={4.Sen}

1.Sen=The recipient will not disclose the {Confidential_Information}, except to {Affiliates}, employees, agents or professional advisors who need to know it and who have agreed in writing (or in the case of professional advisors are otherwise bound) to keep it confidential.

2.Sen=The recipient will ensure that those people and entities use the received {Confidential_Information} only to exercise rights and fulfill obligations under {this Agreement}, while using reasonable care to keep it confidential.

3.Sen=Notwithstanding any provision to the contrary in {this Agreement}, the recipient may also disclose {Confidential_Information} to the extent required by applicable {Legal_Process}; provided that the recipient uses commercially reasonable efforts to: (i) promptly notify the other party of such disclosure before disclosing; and (ii) comply with the other party’s reasonable requests regarding its efforts to oppose the disclosure. Notwithstanding the foregoing, subsections (i) and (ii) above will not apply if the recipient determines that complying with (i) and (ii) could: (a) result in a violation of {Legal_Process}; (b) obstruct a governmental investigation; and/or (c) lead to death or serious physical harm to an individual.

4.Sen=As between the parties, {P2.Handle} is responsible for responding to all third party requests concerning its use and its {End_Users}’ use of the {Services}.